{"tid":1006251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華裔教授發明「神奇薄膜」不用冷氣「溫度就直降17度」震撼科學界","createTime":"2019-02-02T22:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T02:37:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1307,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"e27227cc282481011e4683865540aa1b960f78dc","tid":1006251,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T22:09:39.000Z","msg":"不知不覺間，冬天已經過了一大半。今年的冬天這麼暖和，接下來的夏天會怎麼樣？簡直不敢想像！天氣熱的時候，很多人選擇待在房間里吹冷氣。但一天24小時吹冷氣太耗電，對身體不好，對環境也不好。有什麼簡單、便宜的方法降溫呢？<br />\n<br />\n▼美國科羅拉多大學的2位華裔教授，楊榮貴和尹曉波，發明了一種神奇的薄膜，將它鋪在屋頂，就能輕鬆降溫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0130/20190130040152751.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0130%2F20190130040152751.jpg&h=172c8e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼這種薄膜外表就像保鮮膜，但在顯微鏡下，能夠看到內部有許多直徑僅8微米的玻璃珠，外面則包著透明塑膠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0130/20190130040153389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0130%2F20190130040153389.jpg&h=fde30d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼薄膜由一種名為TPX的塑膠製成。這樣的結構能將陽光反射回去，防止熱量向下滲透。薄膜會將接收的熱量以8到14微米的電磁波形式發射出去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0130/20190130040153260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0130%2F20190130040153260.jpg&h=c5aca6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼這種波長的紅外線不會被大氣層反射、吸收或散射。也就是說，薄膜散發出去的熱量幾乎不會被地球再次吸收，自然就能緩解地球變暖的現象了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0130/20190130040153893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0130%2F20190130040153893.jpg&h=83b8fe15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼這種薄膜的降溫效果非常好。實驗證明，將20㎡的薄膜鋪在屋頂上，在室外37&deg;C的情況下，室內可以保持在20&deg;C左右。薄膜的成本非常低，每平方公尺只需要50美分（約台幣15元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0zvINP6BIj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0zvINP6BIj4&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7gNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=1f48210b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0zvINP6BIj4</a><br />\n<br />\n這種薄膜的製作工藝並不難，很快就能大規模生產，並投入到市場中。這一發明發表到頂級科技雜誌《Science》後，引起了全世界的關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/0130/1239107.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2019%2F0130%2F1239107.html&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7gNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=1f44f420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/0130/1239107.html</a>"},{"pid":"c134684fb4ba5db4a83eb4cbcc544c446e0d5de9","tid":1006251,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":42,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T22:14:06.000Z","msg":"玻璃珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869b5a0406a9e84e2fc2b631a75149e6aa0d822d","tid":1006251,"uid":52215,"like":785,"dislike":2,"score":783,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T22:16:21.000Z","msg":"冷氣佬末日"},{"pid":"91c93e99cb6fc347282619eb22697d193e5f887e","tid":1006251,"uid":47674,"like":1021,"dislike":16,"score":1005,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T22:17:56.000Z","msg":"環保撚表示要走塑 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8898ab64cd2c626fd988b73914bf9ee4160e43e1","tid":1006251,"uid":61280,"like":339,"dislike":5,"score":334,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T22:17:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">OldNews！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/03/061755_32cf90a842ba323df3352d7e6c08005b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F03%2F061755_32cf90a842ba323df3352d7e6c08005b.png&h=c69ebca5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c2ddc4b070e26ce20c4289fae21c1f587e545f2","tid":1006251,"uid":69994,"like":10